PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2008-03232008-02-18,  INDUSTRY,  ,  , 
ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApprove the appointment by the Minister of Industry of LEAH GEORGE-WILSON of North Vancouver, British Columbia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of four years, in the place of Sandra D. White.
